room_title: Escape room "Secret Room of Leonardo da Vinci" by Escape Room Enigma in Chicago
review: Wonderful and kept us on our toes! So many different puzzles to really challenge your critical thinking. Just when you thought you were done, there would be a twist. Truly well thought out!

room_title: Escape room "Secret Room of Leonardo da Vinci" by Escape Room Enigma in Chicago
review: This was a great escape room. Everyone in our group of four had something to do the whole time. Just enough puzzles to keep it both challenging and fun, loved the design as well.
